{"tid":1149460,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"比特幣升穿6700美元　分析料18個月內有望創新高","createTime":"2019-05-11T07:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T13:34:17.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61c4106351579a51660fd7541ef33a33edaeffe1","tid":1149460,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"根據數據平台CryptoCompare資料，虛擬貨幣比特幣升穿6,700美元關，過去24小時由低位6,256.61美元拉升至高見6,787.84美元，最新報6,707.35美元，漲6.8%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年初至今計，比特幣累升約81.2%。如與2017年曾見近2萬美元的歷史高位相比，則仍累跌逾六成。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比特幣大好友、Galaxy Digital創辦人兼行政總裁Michael Novogratz接受外媒採訪時預期，比特幣有望於18個月內突破歷史高位。目前，其下一阻力位將是10,000美元。但由於其他虛擬貨幣如以太幣及瑞波幣的使用範圍不如比特幣，因此料比特幣這次將不會快速上漲。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此前，有分析指比特幣的上升，或與來自投資機構對其交易的興趣逐漸增加有關。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"72f099b0db27c3f2f623cd7649a6bee5a6cccc46","tid":1149460,"uid":31773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢有期貨開始就係比人沽"},{"pid":"26b673e6a562712649b6d3ee3301d4f8318303c2","tid":1149460,"uid":58913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf2ae96501cb3a0aebf0e2be0e4f2aaa6c10222","tid":1149460,"uid":40397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"係咪開始拎左佢來當避險工具"},{"pid":"5a435c417d259243b98a8ce3d43f7964dc6513a6","tid":1149460,"uid":251666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"364473aba9fbca7792f8c48723ac1358fdcc0042","tid":1149460,"uid":73192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf2ae96501cb3a0aebf0e2